/#2-increased-cost-savings-by-the-payment-processing-merchants\" title=\"2. Increased Cost Savings by the payment processing merchants\">2. Increased Cost Savings by the payment processing merchants<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/a-comprehensive-guide-to-corporate-cloud-banking\/#3-banks-cloud-adoption-enables-business-innovation\" title=\"3. Banks cloud adoption enables business innovation\">3. Banks cloud adoption enables business innovation<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/a-comprehensive-guide-to-corporate-cloud-banking\/#the-impact-of-corporate-cloud-banking-on-the-payments-industry\" title=\"The Impact of Corporate Cloud Banking on the Payments Industry\">The Impact of Corporate Cloud Banking on the Payments Industry<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/a-comprehensive-guide-to-corporate-cloud-banking\/#important-drivers-for-adoption-of-cloud-computing-in-the-banking-sector\" title=\"Important Drivers for Adoption of Cloud Computing in the Banking Sector\">Important Drivers for Adoption of Cloud Computing in the Banking Sector<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/a-comprehensive-guide-to-corporate-cloud-banking\/#cloud-computing-and-its-future-in-the-digital-payments-industry\" title=\"Cloud Computing and Its Future in the Digital Payments Industry\">Cloud Computing and Its Future in the Digital Payments Industry<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cloud-computing-in-banking-sector\"><\/span><strong>Cloud Computing in Banking Sector<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The digital payments sector has historically shied away from cloud adoption. Data privacy and security breaches are the primary concerns for businesses in the payments industry due to their heavy regulation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From financial transaction information to daily trading operations, the data handled by payment solution platforms are highly sensitive. If an online <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"182\">payment processing platform<\/a> fails or becomes compromised, it will cause extensive damage to business operations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Potential risks aside, shifting to cloud computing in the banking sector can help banks easily comply with ever-changing regulations, improve customer experience, and drive their growth. Most financial services firms have realized this potential and have started to adopt cloud banking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cloud-computing-helps-to-keep-data-secure.jpg\" alt=\"Corporate Cloud\" class=\"wp-image-416\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cloud-computing-helps-to-keep-data-secure.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cloud-computing-helps-to-keep-data-secure-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cloud-computing-helps-to-keep-data-secure-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"benefits-of-cloud-computing-in-financial-services\"><\/span><strong>Benefits of Cloud Computing in Financial Services<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-cloud-computing-helps-to-keep-data-secure\"><\/span><strong>1. Cloud computing helps to keep data secure<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you look at the digital payments industry, you\u2019ll realize that the large volumes of valuable and highly sensitive financial transaction information transmitted daily easily makes it a target. Therefore, banking as a service needs to use a secure cloud computing platform.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The cloud services used by banks should assist in protecting applications and banking software against automated and targeted hacks. Its protection parameters should <a href=\"https:\/\/www.csoonline.com\/article\/3222095\/ddos-explained-how-denial-of-service-attacks-are-evolving.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">extend to DDoS attacks<\/a> and data breaches.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With cloud technology, companies in the payments industry can rest easy knowing the best cybersecurity experts help protect their client information. The features of cloud services used by banks include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Top-of-the-line security services, including intrusion detection systems, SSL certificates, and DDoS defence.<br>\u2022 Access to modern data centres with advanced tech functions such as physical power and cooling.<br>\u2022 Compliance with all required tech certifications and accreditations<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-increased-cost-savings-by-the-payment-processing-merchants\"><\/span><strong>2. Increased Cost Savings by the payment processing merchants<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Moving from an on-site payments solution to corporate cloud banking allows digital payments firm to shift their focus to operational expenditure (OpEx) from capital expenditure (CapEx). They get to achieve this without having to invest in new IT infrastructure.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Payment processors can enjoy significant cost savings when they shift to cloud banking. Apart from not having to spend on new infrastructure, the elasticity of the cloud means online payment facilitators can manage their operations more efficiently when faced with high traffic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to a report published by <a href=\"https:\/\/home.kpmg\/xx\/en\/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">KPMG<\/a>, banks can save up to 40 per cent after moving their back-office activities to the cloud.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-banks-cloud-adoption-enables-business-innovation\"><\/span><strong>3. Banks cloud adoption enables business innovation<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Financial services companies are facing increasing competition from FinTechs, forcing them to modify their IT approach. The cloud services used by banks have become an indispensable asset that helps to advance networked collaboration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has become commonplace for several teams to access data and documents simultaneously from different locations worldwide. Transmitting financial transaction information to the cloud can significantly increase a company\u2019s innovativeness through enhanced efficiency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, services that previously required up to 14 days to implement can now go live within a few minutes. The opportunity to bring banking as a service to market quickly and securely allows the banking facility to gain a competitive edge over the others.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-impact-of-corporate-cloud-banking-on-the-payments-industry\"><\/span><strong>The Impact of Corporate Cloud Banking on the Payments Industry<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The revolution brought about by big data to payment processing companies has made it possible for them to boost their capacity to mine and access data from any location. Cloud computing has proven to be a superior option that offers unrivalled services to banks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Payments solution providers can access the cloud whenever they want for use cases such as data storage, batch processing, and data analytics. It means that they\u2019re now better placed to utilize resources more efficiently and flexibly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Corporate cloud banking has enabled financial service providers to attain immeasurable gains in <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/blockchain-based-payments-security-analysed\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"126\">cost reduction<\/a> and operational efficiency. Banks only need to pay for the services they use each month, making it more affordable to test products on the cloud.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/The-Impact-of-Corporate-Cloud-Banking-on-the-Payments-Industry.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1078\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/The-Impact-of-Corporate-Cloud-Banking-on-the-Payments-Industry.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/The-Impact-of-Corporate-Cloud-Banking-on-the-Payments-Industry-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/The-Impact-of-Corporate-Cloud-Banking-on-the-Payments-Industry-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"important-drivers-for-adoption-of-cloud-computing-in-the-banking-sector\"><\/span><strong>Important Drivers for Adoption of Cloud Computing in the Banking Sector<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Banking associations worldwide have identified three crucial drivers for the adoption of corporate cloud banking by payment processors:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 Cost benefits: Cloud computing offers significant savings to banks as it eliminates the costs required to acquire modern IT infrastructure.<br>\u2022 Risk mitigation: It helps to reduce the risks linked to traditional computing, e.g., resiliency, redundancy, and capacity concerns.<br>\u2022 Agile innovation: Unlimited access to the cloud means financial institutions have a better chance to innovate by enhancing productivity, efficiency, and agility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The future of cloud computing in banking is boosted by its scalability, which allows it to scan thousands of financial transactions per second. It\u2019s a capability that makes it easier to combat financial crimes such as online money laundering and internet fraud.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cloud-computing-and-its-future-in-the-digital-payments-industry\"><\/span><strong>Cloud Computing and Its Future in the Digital Payments Industry<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Moving forward, cloud computing in the banking sector will continue to grow as banks begin to realize the impact that this technology can have on their operations. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.iif.com\/portals\/0\/Files\/private\/32370132_cloud_computing_in_the_financial_sector_20180803_0.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Institute of International Finance<\/a> states that it\u2019s not a question of if, but how banks will adopt it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The benefits of cloud computing in financial services are immense as it will help banks increase flexibility, reduce operating costs, and promote financial inclusion. However, there\u2019s a need to educate the populace on how it works to boost its uptake.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Industry best practices and enabling policy frameworks will need to be implemented for payment processors to reap the benefits of cloud computing in financial services.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Global digital payments companies fully appreciate the importance of corporate cloud services. Many payment processors are looking for ways on how they can benefit from the innovative potential showcased by this promising technology. Businesses operating in the payments industry sphere have begun to look at the cloud more closely as they become conscious of the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":415,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[23,16,14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/360"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=360"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/360\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1079,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/360\/revisions\/1079"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/415"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=360"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=360"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=360"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}